title: $3400-3/2.5 SW Ft Lauderdale Townhouse-Built 2021-Garage-Fenced Patio
neighborhood: SW Ft Lauderdale - Sailboat Bend - East of I-95
posting_body: ['3 Bedroom, 2.5 Bathroom, 1 Car Garage, 2-Story townhome located within "The Edge on 20th" in Fort Lauderdale.', 'This unit features tile floors throughout, all stainless steel appliances, carpet throughout stairs/second floor, laundry room upstairs, blinds on all windows, ceiling fans, pavers on driveway & private fenced patio.', 'Smart home features include: WiFi garage door opener, Ring doorbell, thermostat, and built in router.', 'One of few lots that allows one car in garage and two in the driveway!', 'Close proximity to Las Olas, Fort Lauderdale Airport, beaches and more.', 'Cat ok with deposit.', 'THIS IS A YEARLY LEASE.', 'Landlord requires First Month, Last Month and Security Deposit to move in (3 month’s rent).', ' Acceptable credit score/report for all persons on the lease (680+), background check and PROOF of income showing sustained combined incomes at least 3 times the amount of the monthly rent.', 'Must have no judgments or money owed to previous landlords.', 'Dianne Warren,', 'show contact info', ', Beachfront Realty.', ' Map view is approximate, not exact, for security reasons.', 'Please CALL to view this property.', ' No texts or emails for first contact.', ' Private owner property.']
